 &lt;p class="display-2 text-uppercase mb-0"&gt;Hero Example&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;div class="pt-3 lead"&gt;
 
 &lt;p&gt;This cover block uses page resources named &lt;code&gt;background&lt;/code&gt; and &lt;code&gt;logo&lt;/code&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class="btn btn-link text-info" href="#td-block-1" aria-label="Read more"&gt;&lt;i class="fa-solid fa-circle-chevron-down" style="font-size: 400%"&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Blocks Lead</title><link>https://meshery-extensions.github.io/tcslabs-academy/pr-preview/pr-48/content-formatting-examples/docsy/blocks-lead/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://meshery-extensions.github.io/tcslabs-academy/pr-preview/pr-48/content-formatting-examples/docsy/blocks-lead/</guid><description>&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-text" data-lang="text"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;{{&amp;lt; blocks/lead color=&amp;#34;primary&amp;#34; height=&amp;#34;min&amp;#34; &amp;gt;}}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;Lead section content here.
